description:
"The game is very simple and has only two rules:
1. After 48 hours, only one boy should be alive in this house.
2. The last two boys who are alive should belong to one team.
Good luck my dear boys. We wish you the best of luck in this weekend.
— Your housekeepers.” © 辛辛息息

description:
Hi guys! This is my story so hope you like it.
Imagine that Lucky is taller than AC

Meet Andree Camille Bonifacio a.k.a Ac. She is great at dancing and she have a bestfriend which is a boy named Reyond Lucky Ancheta or Lucky for short.
AC is kind,smart,talented,beautiful. To make it short, she is almost perfect.

Meet Reyond Lucky Ancheta or Lucky for short. He is also great at dancing that's why him and AC are partners at dancing.
He is kind,handsome,talented and smart like AC.

They both promise to each other that they will never leave each other and not to hide any secrets from each other.

But if one day,both of them realized that they love each other?

Will they hide it from each other or tell it to one another?

Will they still remain their friendship or forget about each other?

Find out if they still remain
 their friendship.



Read the story.*^▁^*♥

description:
Camila Cabello, a disturbed, mental patient, and also known as the Devils favorite in her perspective.

She who tends to be difficult and shows horrendous acts towards others. She who shut the world out. She who is able to express herself in a way of atrocious acts. She who can't be change for what she is. She who can't help anyone but herself. She is a walking disaster. She is the devil himself.

But a new employee, Lauren Jauregui tries work with camila and to try and make a change for her,To cleanse her. 
But it takes more than pills and therapy To Cleanse The Devil.

description:
*SLOW UPDATES* Nearly a year has passed since Eragon left his home of Alagaesia...
He has spent his time since then searching for a new safe haven to raise the riders....When he and Saphira have finally found a suitable place,and have also found the first of the next generation of riders,everything seemed to be going smoothly...But just when they get settled in,a new enemy is brought forth...It will be dangerous and will force Eragon and the riders to take risks and make extreme sacrifices...And it will also bring up dark secrets from a young riders past....

Who will win?....Who will die or survive?......Will they defeat the enemy or will everything go down in flames before it even starts?.....

Everything that belongs to the original Eragon universe belongs to Christopher paolini....anything that isn't part of the original is mine....if you wish to use any aspect of my work then ask me before you do and we shall discuss the "terms of use".....

She dreamed to be like her uncle, finding clues, solve mysteries, and helping people clear their names. What would happen if the famous boy band, One Direction, was accused for something that they didn't do and were being hunt down by the police? What will happen if they meet Belle? Will she willingly help them or will they have to kidnap her? Will the boys clear their names? Full of humor and adventure.

description:
Annie Leonhardt did a bad thing.  
And now she's in prison for it. 

And now she's done another bad thing...

This is the story of the affair between police officer Armin Arlert and inmate Annie Leonhardt. 

Armin was falling in love - but was Annie telling the truth? 

A game is being played, and with time running out, and dangerous people trying to reach her, Annie has big decisions to make. Anything she does from now on will have consequences; and that includes anything related to Armin. 

Will Armin be dragged down Annie's dangerous path? Or will his uncontrollable love for her send him there voluntarily?

description:
​ေငြ​ေၾကးခ်မ္​းသာ​​ေမာက္မာ​၍႐ုပ္​ရည္​ခ​ေလး႐ွိ​ေသာႏႈတ္​ခမ္​းနီမ​ေလးမ်ားရ႕ဲပ့ဲကိုင္​႐ွင္​Central Hotel ပိုင္​႐ွင္​ရ႕ဲသားျဖစ္​သူူ ပိုင္​လင္​းခ👱

လြတ္​လြတ္​လပ္​လပ္​​ေနတတ္​၍နာက္​ဆံုးႏွစ္​တတ္​​ေနၿပီးပိုက္​ဆံ႐ွာ​ေနသူယမင္​းခင္​👩

ယမင္​းထက္​အသက္​နႏွစ္​ႂကီးၿပီးယမင္​းကိုအကိုလို​ေရာသယ္​ခ်င္​းလို​ေရာတဖတ္​သတ္​ခြက္​​ေန​သူသ်ွားသက္​ဟိန္​း👦

description:
Young Elora Nichols wakes up in hospital, not knowing anything about her. The first person she meets is Dr. Carlisle Cullen, the cold but beautiful doctor. Dr. Phillips and Dr. Cullen try to save her life, but at the same time tell her who she is. It proves more difficult than expected, and Elora must choose between her mortal life and an immortal life. The only person stopping her from making her life complete is her father - Gale. With the Volturi following her and Gale following her, she must choose who she wants to defend. Herself, her father, her family, or the love of her life.


*Please note* This is a non-profit fan-fiction. It includes the characters from Twilight and has references to it in the book. I do not own any of the characters who are in the Twilight books, nor do I own the plots that were in the books. All I own is a few characters I made myself and the plot. Credit to ~AwesomeSpyro on DeivantArt for creating the cover, and kindly proof-reading my story before I uploaded it.

description: Hana Kiumori didn't ever have a good life. When she was six her parents were assassinated and she had to virtually disappear before they could find her. In the amazingly famous Ouran Academy she has the second best top score in her second year class just behind Kyoya Otori and just above Tamaki Suou. But that was after she was forced to join the host club on account of being incredibly handsome as a boy. Hana has renamed herself along with her boy-like disguise to a Mr. Ashitaka Modoku. ((author note: fakest sounding name I have ever heard of, sorry.)) Ashitaka or Hana is seen as the Forbidden older brother type. She knows all the girl's want a prince... But life isn't just about Roses and Cakes. No. the S.O.L or the Secret Organization of Lachesis ((anyone? Shit Out of Luck? S.O.L? No?)) Has come to try to kill her at Ouran Academy

description:
When her four year old daughter informs her a sick man is in their yard, Honor Gillette rushes out to help him. But that "sick" man turns out to be Lee Coburn, the man accused of murdering seven people the night before. Dangerous, desperate, and armed, he promises Honor that she and her daughter won't be hurt as long as she does everything he asks. She has no choice but to accept him at his word.

But Honor soon discovers that even those close to her can't be trusted. Coburn claims that her beloved late husband possessed something extremely valuable that places Honor and her daughter in grave danger. Coburn is there to retrieve it -- at any cost. From FBI offices in Washington, D.C., to a rundown shrimp boat in coastal Louisiana, Coburn and Honor run for their lives from the very people sworn to protect them, and unravel a web of corruption and depravity that threatens not only them, but the fabric of our society

description:
"When a person very special to you dies and you know that you are the reason for her death, there's no turning back. It will haunt you in your dreams, forever, but when the death comes straight to you, with a thirst for a really sweet revenge then you'll be haunted even in your awake, and it wouldn't be as sweet as it sounds" 
---
Where 7 people and a girl, plays a game of life, and the game master is the girl. Oh, and the girl is dead too. The story follows 7 popular students of Seiyo Academy, and all of them are tied by a single string that brings them together and closer to death itself. The string is the girl, who has been dead for long, and the game they would be playing is of tag. Cause of the girl's death? the players themselves, of course.

"You'd forever be trailed after by your shadow, dear"

Shugo chara AU
Horror, Paranormal

description:
Roses are Red. Violets are Red. 
Lavender and lemons and oranges are Red.
Fury is Red. Cunning is Red. Deceitful and determined and dauntless is Red.
But afraid is Red. Lost is Red. Missing and wishing and hoping is Red.
~
Red is a closed book, one that no one in Tulsa can seem read. Ponyboy and the others rarely dig up clues from her past life - except that she hasn't had enough to live a normal one. All Red has done for the past two years is travel, searching for the missing puzzle piece in her life. Can Ponyboy figure her out...before she decides to move on?
5,589.

description:
Harry is getting Abused by Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia. It's been going on his whole life. But it becomes worse on the day he get's a letter. I think we all know what letter it is.. And suddenly Harry feels like he is kind of fond of boys.. In a way he is not even accepting himself.. Some other mysterious thing are gonna be happening,  that you are never going to find out in the books. Vampire, Time Lord and a Demon are gonna be mixed in only one person.. Find out who it Is! 



I DO NOT OWN HARRY POTTER, ALL IS THANKS TO MISS J. K. ROWLING, WHO MADE OUR CHILDHOOD MAGICAL!!!! HOPE YOU ENJOY!!!!!

description:
"YAH WHO ARE YOU?! LET ME GO YOU SICK BASTARD!" I screamed in fear as I saw a man covered by his black hoodie.

His mischievous smirk was visible as I was in the state of total shock and trauma since I have been in this situation before.

"Long time no see, 'Jagi'." 

As he said that, I remembered him the man who kidnapped me because he loves me, no, more than obsessed with me. As me, made a total mistake for loving him back.

Being the total stubborn Bitch I am, I escaped away leaving him total broken hearted and dead because he is alone again and his total hard work was just thrown like a total waste.

'I am sorry, I loved you. But, my love for you is very dangerous. You are dangerous, very dangerous. For I shall stop this feelings and mourn for it.'

"Jung--" I haven't continued the thing I was supposed to say because he slapped he hard, very hard that all I see is pitch black.






-An very obsessive Sasaeng who will risk his own life just to make her his.-
